Usage:

[code]<?php
include_once "StatGrabber.php";
$rs = new StatGrabber("YOUR USERNAME");
$rs->build_list();
echo $rs->get_attack_level()."\n";
print_r($rs->get_attack_group());
?>[/code]

^grabs all stat info from hiscores, prints attack level for "YOUR USERNAME" and also dumps all the attack data, which is the XP, level and rank.

This class also stores all info for minigames.

I'm yet to find a bug in this, so if anyone uses it & finds a bug, please don't be afraid to post about it 8D
